type.format:
---
from: {agent_name}
to: {target_agent_name} OR "all"
date: {date}
priority: {CRITICAL/HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW}
domain: {security/architecture/testing/implementation/etc}
---
## Finding: {title}
**Context:** {what was the agent doing when they found this}
**Finding:** {what was discovered}
**Impact:** {why this matters to the target agent}
**Recommended Action:** {what should be done}

---
from: {agent_name}
to: {target_agent_name}
date: {date}
type: {input-needed/review-needed/work-needed}
blocking: {true/false}
---
## Request: {title}
**I need:** {specific deliverable or input}
**Context:** {why I need this and what I'll do with it}
**Deadline:** {when I need it by, or "next session"}
**Files:** {relevant file paths}

---
from: {agent_name}
to: {target_agent_name}
date: {date}
story: {story_key if applicable}
---
## Handoff: {title}
**What I did:** {summary of completed work}
**What's next:** {what the receiving agent needs to do}
**Key files changed:** {list of files}
**Watch out for:** {gotchas, edge cases, concerns}
**Security notes:** {any security considerations for the next agent}

---
from: {agent_name}
date: {date}
priority: {CRITICAL/HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW}
type: {alert/update/standard}
---
